node.text: Полинка, я тоже сначала не хотела в это верить, но сейчас видимо такое время что зарбатывают на всем, попробовала получилось, вчера 68895рyб перевели на карту, если интересно смотри у меня на стрничке.

OMG @anyware_kids just got Platinum for Best Newcomer at the @juniormagazineonline Design Awards !! Delighted and so so proud of this brilliant woman @ggredd - Thank you @juniormagazineonline for this. Means so much. Congrats to all the winners. X #anywarekids #juniordesignawards
😘😘😘😘😘😘 Beyond honored!!!!! Well done us. So proud
Congratulations. What a beautiful performance today - moved me to tears. Thankyou ❤️
AHH congratulations! So lovely to meet you both! Thanks for the beautiful performance Jessie! @anyware_kids ♥️
Congratulations...@anyware_kids is so beautiful... and what an incredible treat to listen to you sing. Thank you! 💫❤️
Wonderful to meet you at the JDA and such a treat to hear your beautiful voice 💖 Congrats for coming top of the class! 👏 x
Massive congratulations and such a treat to hear you singing today! ⭐️
Well done! Where is that lovely dress from Jessie? ❤️
Thank you for coming today and congratulations again on winning a #jda19 🏆👏 and THANK YOU @jessieware for singing with such passion! Made our day 👏😘💕🏆
Amazing!! Well done ladies 🥰 Lovely to meet you xx
Huge congrats. My daughter loves her smock dress. ❤️
